02:39.464 --> 02:40.533
He's home.

02:40.705 --> 02:41.751
Home?

02:42.439 --> 02:43.829
With his parents.

02:44.505 --> 02:46.202
It's okay. It's just another dream.

02:47.099 --> 02:48.259
I have a...

02:48.579 --> 02:49.735
bad feeling.

02:51.071 --> 02:53.090
Kyle's okay.
There's nothing to worry about.

02:53.170 --> 02:54.205
Come on.

